attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Create IOS XR telemetry configuration to stream ISIS data to 192.0.2.10 port 57500 using grpc tls."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group ISIS-INFO
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-agent-oper:xtc/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv4-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/igp-information/igp/isis
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-agent-oper:xtc/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv6-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/igp-information/igp/isis
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-oper:pce/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv4-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/srgb-information/node-id/igp/isis
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-oper:pce-topology/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv4-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/srgb-information/node-id/igp/isis
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-oper:pce/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv6-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/srgb-information/node-id/igp/isis
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 192.0.2.10
    port 57500
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-ISIS
  sensor-group-id ISIS-INFO sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
